(9, 3, 'PHP String Count Specific Character', 'php-string-count-specific-character', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 55); font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">I will give you very simple example of count specific characters in php string. we will use php&nbsp;</span><span class=\"highlighter\" style=\"font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; background: rgb(244, 247, 245); color: rgb(59, 99, 56); padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 18px;\">substr_count()</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 55); font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;function to count words or characters from string in php.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 55); font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-filename=\"download.png\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 55); font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 55); font-family: &quot;crimson text&quot;; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span><br></p>', NULL, 'php', 'I will give you very simple example of count specific characters in php string. we will use php substr_count() function to count words or characters from string in php.', 'I will give you very simple example of count specific characters in php string. we will use php substr_count() function to count words or characters from string in php.', 0, 1, '2023-07-12 03:43:08', '2023-07-12 03:43:08'),
